'15:18': [
{sup:"1a", word:"reign", vrefs:"Psa. 10:16; 29:10; 146:10; Dan. 2:44; Rev. 11:15", lines:["God&rsquo;s habitation, God&rsquo;s house, brings in God&rsquo;s kingdom, God&rsquo;s reign. Today the church is first God&rsquo;s house and then His kingdom ({1Ti3:15|1&nbsp;Tim. 3:15}; {Rom14:17|Rom. 14:17}). The church brings in God&rsquo;s kingdom to the earth ({Eph2:19|Eph. 2:19}; {Mat16:18|Matt. 16:18}-{Mat16:19|19}). Thus, vv. {Exo15:1|1}-{Exo15:18|18} indicate that the goal of God&rsquo;s salvation is the building of His dwelling place for the establishing of His kingdom."]},
],
